data.description: SELLERS NOW OFFERING $5000 CREDIT TO ANY BUYER THAT BRINGS AN ASKING PRICE OFFER! SELLERS ARE MOTIVATED, MAKE AN OFFER TODAY. Welcome home! This property has been well maintained and gently used. purchased as a vacation home and hardly ever stayed in for its last 12 years of ownership. New AC in 2022 and everything else is in like new condition. This property has a fenced in backyard on a corner lot leaving you plenty of private space for storage, entertainment, pets, and more. Property to be sold mostly furnished but is negotiable. Located between Gunnery Rd and Sunshine Blvd, 3 minutes to Lee Blvd, and 15 minutes from I-75 and Fort Myers. Close to shopping, dining, entertainment, and schools! Come check out this property before it's gone.
